Who is the top spending customer and how much is the average price per single item purchased by this customer? What currency was being used?
SELECT avg(Price / Amount) FROM transactions_1k WHERE CustomerID = ( SELECT CustomerID FROM transactions_1k ORDER BY sum(Price / Amount) DESC LIMIT 1 )	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
